## My process

### Built with

- Semantic HTML5 markup
- CSS custom properties
- Flexbox
- Mobile-first workflow

### What I learned

By working on this project I learned how to make a font responsive without using media queries.

```css
:root {
  --font-size-large: clamp(1.25rem, 5vw, 1.5rem); 
  --font-size-medium: clamp(0.875rem, 4vw, 1rem);
  --font-size-small: clamp(0.75rem, 3vw, 0.875rem);
}
```

